{"tid":1988244,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"救命 好似生咗粒牙瘡","createTime":"2020-04-25T05:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T06:07:45.000Z","uid":319100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16d9da4209233986e550bd7154a38b935e8758cd","tid":1988244,"uid":319100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"呢幾日大牙下面突起咗一舊野 有少少黃色咁<br />\n如無意外就應該係牙瘡 <br />\n上網睇好似話生得呢樣野啲牙已經好大穫<br />\n但係我整佢又唔會痛架喎 <br />\n好撚驚 我唔想杜牙根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又貴<br />\n我老豆話佢以前生過揾醫生抽翻啲膿出嚟就冇事 唔洗杜<br />\n有冇人試過生完牙瘡而又冇杜牙根就好翻？<br />\n<br />\n利申 已book牙醫 希望只係小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6dce55443d6a71c9ff3454d8c2d0afc729cd83","tid":1988244,"uid":27824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"快啲去睇牙醫<br />\nbtw可唔可以之後係度講返係咩事"},{"pid":"0331da6fc9fc190debc605859d836afaf53215dd","tid":1988244,"uid":319100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6dce55443d6a71c9ff3454d8c2d0afc729cd83","tid":1988244,"uid":27824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"快啲去睇牙醫<br />\nbtw可唔可以之後係度講返係咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"可以呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />book咗禮拜一"},{"pid":"4224dacbd34a020e7a74e3767782830b118d048d","tid":1988244,"uid":215201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"牙瘡係因為你蛀牙蛀得好深<br />\n有菌入咗牙腳 所以就腫哂 <br />\n同埋你用果邊咬野咬到某啲位應該會痛<br />\n除咗杜牙根就係剝咗佢咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙痛慘過大病 呢啲錢係要比咖<br />\n最緊要係醫生杜得妹周乾淨 <br />\n如果唔係你又黎過<br />\n<br />\n利伸 年輕時做過年幾牙醫助護"},{"pid":"808b30bb76f97eb319ccc0654f61b7c9e575b02f","tid":1988244,"uid":319100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4224dacbd34a020e7a74e3767782830b118d048d","tid":1988244,"uid":215201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"牙瘡係因為你蛀牙蛀得好深<br />\n有菌入咗牙腳 所以就腫哂 <br />\n同埋你用果邊咬野咬到某啲位應該會痛<br />\n除咗杜牙根就係剝咗佢咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙痛慘過大病 呢啲錢係要比咖<br />\n最緊要係醫生杜得妹周乾淨 <br />\n如果唔係你又黎過<br />\n<br />\n利伸 年輕時做過年幾牙醫助護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"咁大穫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我食野用嗰邊咬係完全冇痛喎"}]}